window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Can a villain's power be used for good?</b></p> <p>Toby Gray never thought he'd need to know the answer to that question. Yet after a strange encounter with the world's strongest villain, he finds the course of his life changed forever.</p> <p>When the stars vanish and heroes follow suit, it seems there’s no one left to try to stop an unseen power from taking over the world. But nobody was counting on Toby, a seemingly normal man, to get involved.</p> <p>Once upon a time, he might have refused his hero's call. With an overwhelming power of his own and new friends who are counting on him, he's drawn the line in the sand. He will stop this reign of chaos, one way or another.</p> <p>The fact that it gets him close with a couple of pretty girls, well...that’s just a bonus.</p>"; 
